snippet.title: Airmen Expedition Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Airmen now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/647740/Airmen/

Airmen is a first person shooter where players build and battle their own custom airships. Start with an empty hangar and build a steampunk airship piece by piece. Crew you airship solo or alongside friends on dangerous expeditions into the archipelago.

Stay up to date at...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AirborneGames
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Airmen/
Discord: https://discord.gg/TmxechG
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/647740/Airmen/

Music "Hey Sailor" by Letter Box
